<db:para>The Qml <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtqml-workerscript-workerscript.xml">WorkerScript</db:link> module enables the use of threads in a Qt Quick application.</db:para>
<db:para>Use <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtqml-workerscript-workerscript.xml">WorkerScript</db:link> to run operations in a new thread. This is useful for running operations in the background so that the main GUI thread is not blocked.</db:para>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtqml-workerscript-workerscript.xml">WorkerScript</db:link> supports passing messages between the new thread and the parent thread.</db:para>
<db:para>To use the types in this module, import the module with the following line:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="qml">import QtQml.WorkerScript
</db:programlisting>
